    "The length of the latus rectum of $x^{2} + 3y^{2} = 12$ is"
  ],
  "choices": [
    [
      "$\\frac{2}{\\sqrt{3}}$ units"
    ],
    [
      "$\\frac{1}{3}$ units"
    ],
    [
